spec_data.Name: php-paragonie-constant-time-encoding
spec_data.Description:
Based on the constant-time base64 implementation made by Steve "Sc00bz"
Thomas, this library aims to offer character encoding functions that do not
leak information about what you are encoding/decoding via processor cache
misses.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:25:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Constant-Time Character Encoding in PHP Projects
